<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Magic Link Login</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Kori</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>üîê Your Magic Link</h2>
      <p>Hi{{#if name}} {{name}}{{/if}}!</p>
      <p>Click the button below to sign in to your account. This link will expire in <strong>15 minutes</strong>.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{link}}" class="button">Sign In to Kori</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        Or copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
        <span style="word-break: break-all;">{{link}}</span>
      </p>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Note:</strong> This link can only be used once. If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Kori - Photography Business Manager</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
        If you didn't request this email, please ignore it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>